                        "displayName": "Pal",
                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "Etc/UTC"
                    },
                    "body": "Hi,\r\n\r\nI encounter the same issue. I have a dataset with some character strings non-UTF8. The dataset works fine under Arrow 2.0.0 but not with 3 or 4. When I read those columns I get \"Erreur : Invalid: Invalid UTF8 payload\".\r\n\r\nHow can I fix this issue without rebuilding the dataset ?\r\n\r\nThanks",
